<br>
I am not berating you miss - I often tend to pad things in my favor - actually do it most times heh. My suggestion -- If you know the P.O. Box that the check is going to -- get a friend to camp it (NOT YOU) and have them photograph your ex picking up the mail and then follow him to his address . . . and photograph his home - that way you have an address<br>
<br>
Then turn it into the childsupport folks -- you need to do some of the leg work -- the cops and CS people are so undermanned that all they can do is work on the abuse cases ie those they know are life-threatening to the children.<br>
<br>
Sorry to be a hardass - I know how it feels - my ex-wife didn't pay child support for nine months and I had to do some of the leg work . . . result?<br>
<br>
The court called her in and told her - pay back CS of 3k or go to jail right then . . . She sold a brand new truck - took out a loan and gave me 3k.<br>
<br>
Goodluck<br>
